  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, your soul becomes host to the otherworldly energies of the harrow. You gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Damage-Reduction-Ex-or-Su-\">DR</a>&nbsp;10/<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/special-materials#TOC-Iron-Cold\">cold iron</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Immunity-Ex-or-Su-\">immunity</a>&nbsp;to curses,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Paralysis\">paralysis</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/s/sleep\">sleep</a>. You can always act in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Surprise\">surprise</a>&nbsp;round of combat, and you cannot be caught&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Flat-Footed\">flat-footed</a>. You gain unlimited use of your invoke the harrow ability.</p>"
